trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce un listener che indirizza tutto traccia e debug per il [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] dell'infrastruttura.

trans-unit.source: The IisTraceListener class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: La classe IisTraceListener connette il meccanismo di traccia di [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] a [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe di listener consente agli sviluppatori che creano [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applicazioni e che implementano il <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>e <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interfacce per la generazione di eventi a livello di pagina, modulo o gestore per il [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastruttura durante la traccia è abilitata.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Questa classe listener indirizza [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] eventi alle classi ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Ciò include la <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>classe e le classi che implementano il <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>o <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interfaccia.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page>
